import React, { Component } from 'react' import {Card, Button,Table} from 'react-bootstrap' import {deleteComplient,UpdateComplient} from './../../service/complientService' import { Confirm } from 'semantic-ui-react' export default class ComplientCard extends Component { constructor(props) { super(props) this.state = { open:false } } DeleteOnClick =async(id)=>{ this.open(); const response = await deleteComplient(id) } ChangeState =async(id)=>{ const response = await UpdateComplient(this.props.data._id) } open = () => this.setState({ open: true }) close = () => this.setState({ open: false }) render() { return (
Complient {this.props.data.message}
Mobile: {this.props.data.mobile}
N.I.C: {this.props.data.nic}
Email: {this.props.data.email}
Issue Mobile: {this.props.data.imobile}
Address: {this.props.data.address}
Name: {this.props.data.name}
) } }
